  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      the aim of the study is to correlate between the severity of sepsis and serum heparin binding&#xD;
      protein in the patients admitted to ICU with sepsis., and detect its value as a prognostic&#xD;
      biomarker in sepsis&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
